data.description: This adorable 3-bedroom, 2 bath, pride of ownership home is located in a great SW Visalia neighborhood. Boasting an array of modern upgrades and an open floor plan, this home is designed to cater to your every need. Step into the spacious living area with vaulted ceilings & addition, perfect for home office or additional living space. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living room, dining room, and kitchen - featuring a walk-in pantry, tile countertops, and bar top seating. The spacious master bedroom includes two closets & ensuite featuring a walk-in shower and his & her sinks. The private backyard is complete with a sparkling pool, an above-ground spa, and a gazebo. The property also features RV parking with electricity hookup. Other features include a new A/C unit, solar energy, new flooring throughout, new fencing around the property, new pool pump and filter & keyless entry. Conveniently located to schools, shopping, and restaurants, this SW Visalia home has it all. Schedule your showing today!
